description:
This is a 10 minute workout called '10 Minute Guided Breathing Meditation' from the channel Great Meditation.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation and Rest/Breathing exercises.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This Original 10 minute guided meditation recorded by us, will bring you into a peaceful state with just you and your breath.  Within just a few moments, with a focus on your breathing can heighten your mindfulness and clarity of the mind.  Enjoy!

Spoken Voice: Original Commentary recorded by us.
